## 14. Glossary

| Term | Meaning |
|---|---|
| **Org** | A tenant — one customer business in the `organizations` table. |
| **Cohost** | A profile assigned to one or more properties via `property_cohosts`. Either has `role = 'cohost'`, or any role + at least one `property_cohosts` row. |
| **Manager** | Catch-all for "admin OR cohost". Used by `getUserAccess` to decide whether to show the management UI vs the employee agenda. |
| **Pending invitation** | A `profiles` row whose `invitation_status` is not NULL. The user has been invited to an org but hasn't accepted yet. RLS uses `pending_org_id` so they can see their target org's data after signup. |
| **Magic link QR** | A QR code that encodes a one-time login URL for a phone-only employee. |
